tip.text: Great Christmas dinner on the 24th. The samosa starter was unbelievably good.
Really good vegetarian options. Favorites: Grilled, green peppers and the mushroom ragout.
Don't think the window seats are taken just because it crowded in front. Best seats are way back.
Hands down, best cappuccino I've ever had.
Simply not good enough. Great venue but the food was below mediocre.
Fabulous place to bring a 7 and an 11 year old and talk about architecture and compare Amsterdam to their home city.
